<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_504_line_1592200000174_1105"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Ludwıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> bey Reyn des <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l2"><expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> Reıchs Ercʒtruchſeſſ vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> ın peyern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
</div>
