<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_504_r1l4"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> wır <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> Jobs <expan>Kapf<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l5"><expan>ſchreıb<ex>er</ex></expan> . dem wır befolhen <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . mıt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>red<ex>en</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l6">den ſachen dıe ſıch <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l7"><expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> haben / vnd auch von des neẅen ʒolles <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den man </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l8">in dem lande ʒu <expan>franke<ex>n</ex></expan> vnterſteen meynt <expan>ʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l9"><expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade mıt fleıſſ . was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l10">den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ſachen ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_504_r1l11"><expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan> . Daʒ eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> Jn darinn <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> . Jm </ab>
